              </li>
            
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-purple-500 font-black">•</span>
                <span>Every surface in an Ames Room is distorted, including floor tiles which are skewed trapezoids that look like regular squares.</span>
              </li>
            
